---
---
<section class="section areas">
  <header class="section-header">
    <div>
      <p class="section-eyebrow">§ 02 — Practice areas</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Where I spend <em>my time.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <span class="section-num-big" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
  </header>
  <div class="areas-list">
    <article class="area-row reveal">
      <span class="area-num">01</span>
      <div class="area-content">
        <h3 class="area-title">Airline &amp; aviation digital</h3>
        <p class="area-desc">Mobile experience. Booking flow conversion. Customer-facing platforms that need to hold up under regulatory scrutiny.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="area-loc">AU · SG · MY · NZ</span>
    </article>

    <article class="area-row reveal delay-1">
      <span class="area-num">02</span>
      <div class="area-content">
        <h3 class="area-title">Fintech &amp; regulated finance</h3>
        <p class="area-desc">Teams working through MAS, APRA and RBI frameworks. Platform modernization that has to clear compliance before it ships.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="area-loc">SG · AU · IN</span>
    </article>

    <article class="area-row reveal delay-2">
      <span class="area-num">03</span>
      <div class="area-content">
        <h3 class="area-title">Healthcare digital modernization</h3>
        <p class="area-desc">Operators moving patient-facing systems forward without breaking what's already working. Quietly one of the most complex spaces to operate in.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="area-loc">APAC</span>
    </article>

    <article class="area-row reveal delay-3">
      <span class="area-num">04</span>
      <div class="area-content">
        <h3 class="area-title">CMMI Level 5 partnerships</h3>
        <p class="area-desc">Connecting IT services firms with certified Level 5 partners for government and enterprise bids that require process maturity.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="area-loc">Global</span>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .areas-list { padding-bottom: 8px; }
  .area-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr auto;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    transition: padding 0.5s var(--ease-out-expo), background 0.4s var(--ease-out);
    position: relative;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .area-row:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .area-row::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 22px;
    bottom: 22px;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: top;
    transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .area-row:hover {
    padding-left: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-mark), transparent 60%);
  }
  .area-row:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }

  .area-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent);
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .area-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .area-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.6vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.4s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .area-row:hover .area-title { color: var(--accent); }
  .area-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .area-loc {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .area-row {
      grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .area-loc { grid-column: 2; padding-top: 0; margin-top: 4px; }
    .area-row:hover { padding-left: 8px; }
  }
</style>
